{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"4806","heading":"National Pork Producers Delegate Body","label":"4806 National Pork Producers Delegate Body","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/ch79","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","Effective DateSection effective , see , set out as a note under .Jan. 1, 1986section 1631 of Pub. L. 99–198section 4801 of this title"],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Establishment and appointment","label":"a Establishment and appointment","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The order shall provide for the establishment and appointment by the Secretary, not later than 60 days after the effective date of such order, of a National Pork Producers Delegate Body.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Membership; number of producer members; number of importer members","label":"b Membership; number of producer members; number of importer members","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fb%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/1/A/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/1/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fb%2F1%2FA%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"in the case of the initial Delegate Body appointed by each State in accordance with .section 4807 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/1/A/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/1/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fb%2F1%2FA%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subclause","nativeType":"subclause","number":"I","heading":null,"label":"I","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/1/A/ii/I","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/1/A/ii","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fb%2F1%2FA%2Fii%2FI","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"is approved by the Secretary;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subclause","nativeType":"subclause","number":"II","heading":null,"label":"II","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/1/A/ii/II","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/1/A/ii","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fb%2F1%2FA%2Fii%2FII","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"requires public notice of the process to be given at least one week in advance by publication in a newspaper or newspaper of general circulation in such State and in pork production and agriculture trade publications; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subclause","nativeType":"subclause","number":"III","heading":null,"label":"III","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/1/A/ii/III","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/1/A/ii","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fb%2F1%2FA%2Fii%2FIII","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"that provides complete and equal access to the nominating process to every producer who has paid all assessments due under and not demanded a refund under ,section 4809 of this titlesection 4813 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"iii","heading":null,"label":"iii","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/1/A/iii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/1/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fb%2F1%2FA%2Fiii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"In the case of a State that has a State association that does not submit nominations or that does not have a State association, such State shall submit nominations in a manner prescribed by the Secretary; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fb%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"importers, as appointed by the Secretary in accordance with paragraph (3).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fb%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/2/A/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/2/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fb%2F2%2FA%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"for the 1986 calendar year, on the basis of one share for each $400,000 of farm market value of porcine animals marketed from such State (as determined by the Secretary based on the annual average of farm market value in the most recent 3 calendar years preceding such year), rounded to the nearest $400,000; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/2/A/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/2/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fb%2F2%2FA%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"for each calendar year thereafter, on the basis of one share for each $1,000 of the aggregate amount of assessments collected (minus refunds under ) in such State from persons described in section 4809(a)(1)(A) and (B) of this title, rounded to the nearest $1,000.section 4813 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fb%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/2/B/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/2/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fb%2F2%2FB%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"less than 301, the State shall receive a total of two producer members;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/2/B/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/2/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fb%2F2%2FB%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"more than 300 but less than 601, the State shall receive a total of three producer members;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"iii","heading":null,"label":"iii","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/2/B/iii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/2/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fb%2F2%2FB%2Fiii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"more than 600 but less than 1,001, the State shall receive a total of four producer members; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"iv","heading":null,"label":"iv","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/2/B/iv","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/2/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fb%2F2%2FB%2Fiv","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"more than 1,000, the State shall receive four producer members, plus one additional member for each 300 additional shares in excess of 1,000 shares, rounded to the nearest 300.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fb%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/3/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fb%2F3%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/3/A/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/3/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fb%2F3%2FA%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"for the 1986 calendar year, on the basis of one share for each $575,000 of market value of marketed porcine animals, pork, or pork products (as determined by the Secretary based on the annual average of imports in the most recent 3 calendar years preceding such year), rounded to the nearest $575,000; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/3/A/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/3/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fb%2F3%2FA%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"for each calendar year thereafter, on the basis of one share for each $1,000 of the aggregate amount of assessments collected (minus refunds under ) from importers, rounded to the nearest $1,000.section 4813 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/3/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fb%2F3%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/3/B/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/3/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fb%2F3%2FB%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"three members for the first 1,000 such shares; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/3/B/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/b/3/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fb%2F3%2FB%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"one additional member for each 300 additional shares in excess of 1,000 shares, rounded to the nearest 300.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Voting; quorum; votes necessary for decision","label":"c Voting; quorum; votes necessary for decision","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/c/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/c/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fc%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the number of shares attributable to the State of the member; divided by","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/c/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/c/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fc%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the number of producer members from such State.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/c/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fc%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/c/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/c/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fc%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the number of shares allocated to importers; divided by","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/c/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/c/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fc%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the number of importer members.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/c/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fc%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Members entitled to cast a majority of the votes (including fractions thereof) on the Delegate Body shall constitute a quorum.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/c/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fc%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"A majority of the votes (including fractions thereof) cast at a meeting at which a quorum is present shall be decisive of a motion or election presented to the Delegate Body for a vote.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"d","heading":"Term of office","label":"d Term of office","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/d","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fd","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"A member of the Delegate Body shall serve for a term of 1 year, except that the term of a member of the Delegate Body shall continue until the successor of such member, if any, is appointed in accordance with subsection (b)(1).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"e","heading":"Chairman","label":"e Chairman","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/e","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fe","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/e/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/e","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fe%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"At the first annual meeting, the Delegate Body shall select a Chairman by a majority vote.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/e/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/e","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fe%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"At each annual meeting thereafter, the President of the Board shall serve as the Chairman of the Delegate Body.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"f","heading":"Compensation","label":"f Compensation","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/f","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Ff","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"A member of the Delegate Body shall serve without compensation, but may be reimbursed by the Board from assessments collected under for transportation expenses incurred in performing duties as a member of the Delegate Body.section 4809 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"g","heading":"Nomination of members to National Pork Board; annual meeting; majority vote in person to nominate","label":"g Nomination of members to National Pork Board; annual meeting; majority vote in person to nominate","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/g","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fg","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/g/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/g","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fg%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/g/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/g/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fg%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/g/1/A/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/g/1/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fg%2F1%2FA%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"not less than 23 persons for appointment to the Board, for the first year for which nominations are made; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/g/1/A/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/g/1/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fg%2F1%2FA%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"not less than 1½ persons (rounded up to the nearest person) for each vacancy in the Board that requires nominations thereafter; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/g/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/g/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fg%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"submit such nominations to the Secretary.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/g/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/g","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fg%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Delegate Body shall meet annually to make such nominations.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/g/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/g","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fg%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"A majority of the Delegate Body shall vote in person in order to nominate members to the Board.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"h","heading":"Duties and functions","label":"h Duties and functions","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/h","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fh","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/h/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/h","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs4806%2Fh%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"recommend the rate of assessment prescribed by the initial order and any increase in such rate pursuant to section 4809(5) of this title; and1So in original. Probably should be section “4809(b)”.1","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s4806/h/2","parentIdentifier":